    (uuid "f4aff105-c668-4b08-b251-7d925c988534"))
  (text "1. OHIS Grounds: MicGND (Pin3), HPGND (Pin5), PwrGND (Pin7) are separate copper pours." (at 10 282 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.0 1.0)))
    (uuid "8bac40fd-3821-42f5-b14b-3baca3a089da"))
  (text "   Joins only at star-ground point near power supply. Do NOT merge on PCB traces." (at 10 287 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.0 1.0)))
    (uuid "921db1fb-6a68-4fcd-bb90-677ca13c6ec4"))
  (text "2. NAU8822 I2C address: CSB/CSIF pin=GND → address 0x1A. NAU8822 datasheet Table 10." (at 10 294 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.0 1.0)))
    (uuid "ee5d1633-356a-4618-9125-50f419b0b305"))
  (text "3. MCLK: 12.288MHz = 256*Fs (48kHz). Oscillator OE pin HIGH=enabled, tie to +3V3." (at 10 299 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.0 1.0)))
    (uuid "95dc73d5-858b-4b31-8683-37ad279650ca"))
  (text "4. BTN_DOWN uses pull-UP (GPIO15 strapping pin must be HIGH at boot for normal operation)." (at 10 304 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.0 1.0)))
    (uuid "e1fd05e6-0fd1-44dc-b3ba-ef43c075c02d"))

